data.description: This Ranch home with basement and Pole Barn sits on 2 acres located in Winfield Twsp. with Crown Point schools New kitchen with beautiful quartz counter tops, tiled backsplash and lighted upper cabinets. All appliances stay Great room with fireplace and open stairwell to lower level. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with full basement 3/4's finished with bath rough in and the possibility of a 2nd kitchen for related living,(seller is leaving kitchen cabinets, range and refrigerator in lower level). Updates include, new kitchen, windows, furnace, wood flooring, many rooms freshly painted and landscaping.Beautiful 2 acres treelined for privacy with many mature trees and pine trees. 2 storage sheds with a nice 32x24 Pole Barn that is insulated with electric. Agents please read agent remarks.
